{"tid":2057723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：「風險可控」的前提下將逐步取消入境限制","createTime":"2020-06-09T15:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T02:13:40.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"23d02739d8f37a342ea16b96a39ce545c06a3c4f","tid":2057723,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:11:30.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網站表示，按現在持續穩定的疫情和不斷提升的病毒檢測量，<span style=\"color: red;\">預計稍後可以進一步放寬某些社交距離措施，並在風險可控的前提下，逐步取消入境限制和14天強制檢疫的規定</span>。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又指，在統計處最新發布有關中小型企業業務狀況的按月統計調查報告中，中小企業務收益的「現時動向指數」，由今年4月的31.0顯著上升至5月的41.9，其中飲食業升幅最強勁。林鄭月娥指，雖然出現可喜的現象，但距離走出困境，回復正常，仍需一段時間，「保就業計劃」首批完成的僱主申請，中小企業佔98%，預計本周內能陸續收到用作工資補貼的款項。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1304539&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1304539%26csid%3D261_341&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=70364ecd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1304539&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n永續限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2247262de36e0c98b15f162467f0a9f2c899cf","tid":2057723,"uid":4964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"拖到國安法過左,多多蝗都唔怕香港人反抗"},{"pid":"b968954044fe193cd3afda77d08fa53757ad85dc","tid":2057723,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"[抗爭一週年]大鑊!原來今日有個好緊要嘅行動未做!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2057718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2057718</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7bad1c3ef43d553452d4c8a1f66a32a1e9ecbf59","tid":2057723,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a2247262de36e0c98b15f162467f0a9f2c899cf","tid":2057723,"uid":4964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"拖到國安法過左,多多蝗都唔怕香港人反抗"},"citedB